<arggraph id="micro_c198" topic_id="treat_dogs_as_humans" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA["For centuries, dogs have been known as ""man's best friend.""]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[So why should we treat them as less than our equals?]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[They are always there for us, helping us when we need it.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Most dogs are groomed and trained to be dependable,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[so we should be able to rely on them.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[With that logic, we should them be treating them like members of our family.]]></edu>
